01:16:03.370 --> 01:16:06.580
And any electron that
came from this term

01:16:06.580 --> 01:16:09.860
in the superposition
will be kicked up up z.

01:16:09.860 --> 01:16:13.930
And any electron that came
from the superposition down z

01:16:13.930 --> 01:16:15.274
will have down.

01:16:15.274 --> 01:16:17.690
Now, what we really mean is
