in the z direction.

01:18:36.280 --> 01:18:37.482
OK?

01:18:37.482 --> 01:18:39.940
This means that, at the moment,
initially, if I said, look,

01:18:39.940 --> 01:18:42.273
is it going to be up or down
with equal probabilities, 1

01:18:42.273 --> 01:18:44.800
over root 2 with
equal amplitudes,

01:18:44.800 --> 01:18:46.560
if I measure spin in
